# Arbitrum configure step for the new LZ_V3 plugin:
# - register plugin in existing Arbitrum PluginRegistry
# - configure Arbitrum -> OP and Arbitrum -> Base outbound routes
# - trust inbound OP and Base LZ_V3 plugins on the Arbitrum adapter
# - refresh Arbitrum asset trust rows
